transcripts.text: We understand, apparently, this is just coming to me as news as well, that her show has been suspended tonight and did not air over at Fox News Channel.  Sources close to the network telling us that's because she made a very staunch defense of President Trump.  and wanted to expose or attempt to expose the voter fraud that the Republicans and the president, I should say, are claiming took place in the election.  Fox decided not to air Judge Jeanine Pirro's show because that was going to be the content of the program.  It's a Saturday night show.
